  "detailed_description": "<h1>Free updates</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/117a7784c2da151c47411c3fd2b21127.avif?t=1727955262\" width=616 height=78 /></span></p></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><strong>Offroad Mania</strong> — off-road 4x4 driving simulator based on realistic car physics. Regularly free updates!<br><strong>Modes:</strong> Classic (240 levels), Free Roam, Racing, Endless, Winter (rocks, mud, snow, water, logs, trees, bridges, ramps). <br><strong>Vehicles:</strong> 10+ amazing 4×4 cars for your driving fun. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/fdb93a18e238dc7770b2be3bdef36567.avif?t=1727955262\" width=570 height=116 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/e5125f064a210ec41a19ffb3bb96a3aa.avif?t=1727955262\" width=570 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >CLASSIC MODE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/5a0d13830a60e21dd5785ae9e15eeba7.poster.avif?t=1727955262\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/5a0d13830a60e21dd5785ae9e15eeba7.webm?t=1727955262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/6b9da26b72c99731e124a3b389ae1166.poster.avif?t=1727955262\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/6b9da26b72c99731e124a3b389ae1166.webm?t=1727955262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Description:</strong><br>Classic trial on special levels. All levels have a start and a finish line with 3 trophies to grab. No time limit.<br><br><strong>Sub-modes:</strong><br><u>Hard mode</u> - get all trophies in one attempt (or quickly restart with the new GUI).<br><u>Cockpit mode</u> - complete all levels in cockpit view.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREEROAM MODE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/6b82d93511a1c4a083fcc15df840dcc3.poster.avif?t=1727955262\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/6b82d93511a1c4a083fcc15df840dcc3.webm?t=1727955262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Description:</strong><br>Free ride without limitation. No start/finish and no trophies. No time limit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >RACING MODE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/45225b32ed5954c2451bdb9a20d064b7.poster.avif?t=1727955262\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/45225b32ed5954c2451bdb9a20d064b7.webm?t=1727955262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Description:</strong><br>Race tracks with a timer. There is a start/finish line and a global time-leaderboard. No trophies to grab while racing.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >ENDLESS MODE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/309614fcf216a2540034592027277062.poster.avif?t=1727955262\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/309614fcf216a2540034592027277062.webm?t=1727955262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/dda81c9dedf206da0d20322a1472afd4.poster.avif?t=1727955262\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/dda81c9dedf206da0d20322a1472afd4.webm?t=1727955262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Description:</strong><br>Endless road with trophies. No finish line, 1 trophy per short segment of track. Leaderboard available at the end of each run. No time limit.<br><br><strong>Sub-mode:</strong><br><u>Hard mode</u> - endless road with time limit.<br>p.s. Endless mode now generates a track with 130 distinct segments (we will add more with coming updates).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >WINTER MODE</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/4402a23cbf04d14e0b10aef6d133fc43.poster.avif?t=1727955262\" width=600 height=220 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/4402a23cbf04d14e0b10aef6d133fc43.webm?t=1727955262\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Description:</strong><br>Free ride with challenge. No finish line. No trophies. 1 Challenge (snowball). Leaderboard available at the end of challenge. No time limit.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURED</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Classic (240 levels) + Free roam + Racing + Endless + Winter (rocks, mud, snow, water, logs, trees, bridges, ramps)<br></li><li> 10+ amazing 4×4 off road cars (different suspension and chassis setups as well as distinct engine sounds)<br></li><li> Car physics based game<br></li><li> Car and driver customization<br></li><li> Fun driving gameplay<br></li><li> Flat graphics (colorful, clean and HARDWARE FRIENDLY)<br></li><li> Gamepad support</li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FREE UPDATES</h2>We regularly improve the game with you (write your ideas in our Community Hub and Discord channel).<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >GO OFF ROAD! GO HAVE FUN!</h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1222040/extras/013aa5c19ecd37fc5bbce58aca1d2d7e.avif?t=1727955262\" width=616 height=210 /></span>",
